## Rocket Mode (Pilot POV) -- Detailed Implementation Plan

This plan covers five new files and modifications to two existing files. The implementation follows the existing patterns observed throughout the Universe module: ref-based animation loops with `batchDraw()`, single `<Shape>` sceneFunc for batch canvas drawing, glass morphism CSS for HTML overlays, and hooks that return refs/callbacks consumed by layers.

